[Name] Compiz-Fusion
[Summary] A Composite Window Manager resulted from the merge between Beryl and Compiz Extras.
[Description] Compiz Fusion is the result of a merge between the well-known Beryl \
composite window manager and Compiz Extras, a community set of improvements to the \
Compiz composite window manager. Compiz Fusion aims to provide an easy and fun-to-use \
windowed environment, allowing use of the graphics hardware to render each individual \
window and the entire screen, to provide some impressive effects, speed and usefulness.
